text: Haaswood is an unincorporated community in St. Tammany Parish, Louisiana, United States. The community is located north-northeast of Slidell on Louisiana Highway 1091 and miles east of Alton.Louisiana Atlas & Gazetteer, DeLorme, 3rd ed., 2010, p. 48 ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in St. Tammany Parish, Louisiana Category:Unincorporated communities in Louisiana Category:Unincorporated communities in New Orleans metropolitan area
